responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8D4407CF4B8599B80330EE88037FD2B5", "During the Harbinger Apocalypse the dragon Sillasin was said to have entered the fray. Peculiar as it was, he fought both exalted and fiend. Not much was left to record this appearance, yet, a scale from the beast is said to be making the rounds on the black markets of the Riverlands. Keep watch!")
